import Project from "../components/Project"

function Portfolio() {
    return <main>
        <section className="portfolio page">
            <section className="portfolio-main">
                <Project
                    title="Marvel Quiz"
                    github="https://github.com/Anissa1021/marvel-quiz.git"
                    link="https://anissa1021.github.io/marvel-quiz/"
                    image="/React-Portfolio/images/Campricorn.png"
                />
                <Project 
                    title="Note Taker App" 
                    github="https://github.com/Anissa1021/note-taker.git" 
                    link="https://note-taker-ejs-420ed520ac41.herokuapp.com/" 
                    image="/react-portfolio/public/images/pokemon_quiz.png"
                />
                <Project 
                    title="" 
                    github="" 
                    link="https://expressjs-note-taker25.herokuapp.com/" 
                    image="/react-portfolio/public/images/note_taker.png"
                />
                <Project 
                    title="Weather Dashboard" 
                    github="https://github.com/Anissa1021/weather-dash.git" 
                    link="https://anissa1021.github.io/weather-dash/" 
                    image="/react-portfolio/public/images/weather-forecast.png"
                />
            </section>
        </section>
    </main>
}

export default Portfolio;
